7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Lexica and PhotoRoom share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Api Access, Commercial License. On the other hand, PhotoRoom uniquely offers Image To Image and Batch Generation, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Lexica holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while PhotoRoom scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Lexica and PhotoRoom offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Lexica's free tier and PhotoRoom's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
